Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and SW-Checklist Completed across all process variants containing both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Checklist Completed to occur after SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average duration of the period starting with SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and ending with the next non-reminder system activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-Awaiting AE Assignment)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Time elapsed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days, compared with the time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to the subsequent occurrence of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days measured as the interval until SW-Checklist Completed appears in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum waiting time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Checklist Completed in variants that lead to SW-EIC Reject, compared to variants that lead to SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days versus the elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Average time it takes for SW-Checklist Completed to follow SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days in cases where no additional co-author account creation occurs afterward
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to the first appearance of a reviewer assignment activity (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers) in the same trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and Manuscript Export Succeeded when Manuscript Export Succeeded reappears later in the process (e.g., post-acceptance)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in end-to-end accepted manuscript variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Cycle time of SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days defined as the duration from its occurrence to the completion of the entire review process (i.e., final Manuscript Export Succeeded)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
